  "plot outline": "Christine \"Lady Bird\" McPherson (Saoirse Ronan) is a high-school senior from the \"wrong side of the tracks\". She longs for adventure, sophistication, and opportunity, but finds little of that in her Sacramento Catholic high school. Her senior year improves: she finds her first romance, participates in the school play, and--most importantly--applies for college.",
